unittitle_ssm: Dorsey and Whitney, LLP Guantanamo Bay Detention Camp Records
abstract_ssm: This collection documents the detention of six Bahraini men at the Guantanamo Bay Detention Camp and their legal representation by a group of attorneys from the firm of Dorsey & Whitney, LLP.  Included are correspondence, a variety of legal documents, and press from online and print sources.
